    83→class PluginManager:
    84→    """Core class which manages registration of plugin objects and 1:N hook
    85→    calling.
    86→
    87→    You can register new hooks by calling :meth:`add_hookspecs(module_or_class)
    88→    <PluginManager.add_hookspecs>`.
    89→
    90→    You can register plugin objects (which contain hook implementations) by
    91→    calling :meth:`register(plugin) <PluginManager.register>`.
    92→
    93→    For debugging purposes you can call :meth:`PluginManager.enable_tracing`
    94→    which will subsequently send debug information to the trace helper.
    95→
    96→    :param project_name:
    97→        The short project name. Prefer snake case. Make sure it's unique!
    98→    """
